title: 002-Speed.Racer.PAL.WII-crosby
description:
Special Features  

  

Play more than 19 characters from the film featuring the voices of Emile Hirsch as Speed Racer, Matthew Fox as Racer X, and Christina Ricci as Trixie
High-speed action going over 400mph as you race through amazing stadiums tracks featuring loops, corkscrews, jumps and more
Master Car-Fu combat and fight your way to the finish by smashing, jumping, flipping and spinning other cars off the track
Split-screen multi-player racing on the Wii lets you take on - or take out - your friends
Compatible with the Wii Wheel
